      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RACCOON ROGER (4) has a strong record here with four wins and a minor from six starts. Recorded a 2.5 lengths win (21.66) in a Grade 4 last time at this track. Appeals as a leading chance in this. VERRUCKT (1) was in the minors two back (21.88) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 8th. Form here at the trip sound including nine wins. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. BRIDGE UP BABY (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 4 at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. RINGWALD (3) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
